1
00:00:00,740 --> 00:00:04,710
Just remember that the only person
who can stop me is you, Jang Mi.

2
00:00:05,740 --> 00:00:07,050
I won't stop.

3
00:00:08,010 --> 00:00:11,480
Because you're the only one
holding the brakes.

4
00:00:18,760 --> 00:00:19,760
Seo Rin.

5
00:00:26,030 --> 00:00:27,030
Jun Ho.

6
00:00:27,630 --> 00:00:32,370
Do you really love Oh Jang Mi and not me?
Is that it?

7
00:00:32,600 --> 00:00:34,940
No, Seo Rin. It's not like that. I just...

8
00:00:35,010 --> 00:00:37,280
Oh Jang Mi, stay out of this.
I'm asking Jun Ho.

9
00:00:40,380 --> 00:00:42,780
Jun Ho, answer me.

10
00:00:43,550 --> 00:00:46,520
Do you really love Oh Jang Mi?

11
00:00:47,020 --> 00:00:48,020
Yes.

12
00:00:48,750 --> 00:00:50,390
I love her more than anything
in this world.

13
00:00:51,390 --> 00:00:54,760
And I am going to marry her,
no matter what.

14
00:00:58,260 --> 00:00:59,530
(General Manager Kang Jun Ho)

15
00:00:59,630 --> 00:01:00,630
Seo Rin!

16
00:01:01,200 --> 00:01:02,200
Seo Rin!

17
00:01:03,400 --> 00:01:04,400
Seo Rin!

18
00:01:08,310 --> 00:01:11,310
What did you do while I was gone?

19
00:01:11,840 --> 00:01:14,980
What did you do to make
Jun Ho fall for you like this?

20
00:01:15,050 --> 00:01:16,350
I didn't do anything.

21
00:01:16,780 --> 00:01:19,280
I told you, didn't I?
The person I love is Baek Ho.

22
00:01:19,350 --> 00:01:22,050
If you didn't do anything,
is Jun Ho on drugs or something?

23
00:01:22,550 --> 00:01:24,590
Going on about
how he'll see this through to the end,

24
00:01:24,720 --> 00:01:26,620
and that he won't stop loving you...

25
00:01:27,430 --> 00:01:29,860
- Does that even make sense?
- It's driving me crazy, too!

26
00:01:30,130 --> 00:01:32,730
- Please believe me, Seo Rin.
- You're lying to me.

27
00:01:33,300 --> 00:01:35,070
You were even going to marry Jun Ho.

28
00:01:35,400 --> 00:01:38,670
How could you even think of marrying him
if you claim to dislike him so much?

29
00:01:38,840 --> 00:01:40,510
- I told you...
- No,

30
00:01:40,840 --> 00:01:41,970
I don't want to hear it.

31
00:01:43,010 --> 00:01:46,340
Come to think of it,
you planned to take everything from me.

32
00:01:46,710 --> 00:01:49,050
I shouldn't have gone easy on you
just because you're my twin.

33
00:01:49,110 --> 00:01:52,220
I'm not going to let you take anything
from me.

34
00:02:05,500 --> 00:02:07,230
My love.

35
00:02:09,670 --> 00:02:12,440
After losing you and Eun Hye like that,

36
00:02:13,740 --> 00:02:15,970
I don't know
how I can still be breathing...

37
00:02:16,710 --> 00:02:18,610
or how I can go on living like this.

38
00:02:20,950 --> 00:02:23,780
There's just so much going on.

39
00:02:27,690 --> 00:02:28,690
Honey.

40
00:02:29,890 --> 00:02:33,020
Am I being punished?

41
00:02:34,330 --> 00:02:36,660
But at least I found
our Dong Seok's daughters,

42
00:02:38,230 --> 00:02:40,330
the twins.

43
00:02:44,700 --> 00:02:45,700
Honey.

44
00:02:54,810 --> 00:02:55,810
Honey.

45
00:02:56,580 --> 00:02:58,350
What kind of tea would you like?

46
00:02:59,650 --> 00:03:01,690
Jujube tea, ginseng tea,

47
00:03:02,020 --> 00:03:03,990
Ssanghwa tea, green tea, or ginger tea?

48
00:03:07,290 --> 00:03:08,860
Honey, have you been crying?

49
00:03:12,600 --> 00:03:13,900
You have been.

50
00:03:14,470 --> 00:03:15,870
Get out of my face.

51
00:03:17,070 --> 00:03:18,340
Yes, of course.

52
00:03:25,810 --> 00:03:29,710
Grandma, are you making
a four-leaf clover bracelet?

53
00:03:29,750 --> 00:03:31,120
Yes.

54
00:03:31,350 --> 00:03:32,550
You're so pretty, Bo Ra.

55
00:03:32,920 --> 00:03:35,220
I'm making this for you, Bo Ra.

56
00:03:35,220 --> 00:03:36,920
Yes! I'm so excited!

57
00:03:49,300 --> 00:03:52,540
How dare those bastards throw me out?

58
00:03:52,600 --> 00:03:54,870
Please, don't just drink water.
You should eat something.

59
00:03:55,340 --> 00:03:56,570
You'll collapse if you keep this up.

60
00:03:56,910 --> 00:03:58,210
I won't let them get away with this.

61
00:03:58,610 --> 00:04:00,240
I'm going to kill them.

62
00:04:00,380 --> 00:04:02,250
We can't come up with a plan
until you calm down.

63
00:04:02,310 --> 00:04:03,550
A plan? Forget a plan!

64
00:04:03,950 --> 00:04:05,020
Ma'am...

65
00:04:06,220 --> 00:04:09,550
You're right.
There are plenty of things we can do.

66
00:04:10,790 --> 00:04:13,560
Do you think I'll go down that easily?
Fat chance.

67
00:04:14,390 --> 00:04:18,100
I could buy a whole hotel
with my slush fund alone.

68
00:04:19,330 --> 00:04:23,230
That old fool Chairman Ma
picked a fight with the wrong person.

69
00:04:32,010 --> 00:04:33,010
Seo Rin, is that you?

70
00:04:36,210 --> 00:04:39,080
And Jang Mi is behind you, right?
I'm getting dizzy.

71
00:04:39,720 --> 00:04:42,890
- How can you two look so identical?
- Where's Grandfather?

72
00:04:42,950 --> 00:04:46,160
He just went in to get some shut-eye.

73
00:04:53,600 --> 00:04:55,970
Seo Rin, please. You've got it all wrong.

74
00:04:56,070 --> 00:04:58,770
Why were you looking for Grandfather?

75
00:04:59,500 --> 00:05:01,070
You were going to tell him...

76
00:05:01,470 --> 00:05:03,010
Jun Ho was my mom's son, weren't you?

77
00:05:03,140 --> 00:05:06,980
Grandfather needs to know exactly
what Chae Hwa Young's intentions were.

78
00:05:07,580 --> 00:05:10,350
That she planned to use Jun Ho
to take over Dream.

79
00:05:10,580 --> 00:05:13,020
And that's why she tried
to marry one of us off to Jun Ho.

80
00:05:13,180 --> 00:05:14,320
Shut it.

81
00:05:14,550 --> 00:05:16,320
I'm done listening to your twisted logic.

82
00:05:17,320 --> 00:05:18,320
Seo Rin.

83
00:05:22,190 --> 00:05:24,460
Okay, fine. I'll believe you.

84
00:05:25,130 --> 00:05:26,130
But in return,

85
00:05:26,830 --> 00:05:27,830
I have a favor to ask.

86
00:05:29,070 --> 00:05:31,140
- What is it?
- You have to keep...

87
00:05:31,570 --> 00:05:34,240
Jun Ho being my mom's son a secret
from Grandfather.

88
00:05:34,770 --> 00:05:35,770
What?

89
00:05:36,070 --> 00:05:38,740
Jun Ho already knows
that Chae Hwa Young is his mother.

90
00:05:39,380 --> 00:05:41,410
- And you want me to keep it a secret?
- Yes.

91
00:05:41,850 --> 00:05:43,450
If Grandfather finds out the truth,

92
00:05:44,420 --> 00:05:46,120
he'll kick Jun Ho out of the company.

93
00:05:46,750 --> 00:05:47,750
I don't want that to happen.

94
00:05:48,420 --> 00:05:50,190
No, more than anything,

95
00:05:50,960 --> 00:05:53,060
I can't marry Jun Ho now.

96
00:05:53,930 --> 00:05:56,190
- I might not even see him again.
- Ma Seo Rin.

97
00:05:57,200 --> 00:06:00,000
Don't look at me like that.
Do you feel sorry for me?

98
00:06:00,630 --> 00:06:01,630
Shit.

99
00:06:02,630 --> 00:06:05,040
Even if he likes you and not me,

100
00:06:05,540 --> 00:06:07,670
I'll take him from you. It's that simple.

101
00:06:07,940 --> 00:06:09,440
I'm never giving him up to you.

102
00:06:10,270 --> 00:06:11,540
So just keep your mouth shut.

103
00:06:12,180 --> 00:06:14,450
So keep Jun Ho being
my mom's biological son a secret.

104
00:06:15,910 --> 00:06:17,150
Answer me, Oh Jang Mi!

105
00:06:20,790 --> 00:06:22,050
Even if I don't say anything,

106
00:06:22,650 --> 00:06:24,520
this secret is going to come out
sooner or later.

107
00:06:25,290 --> 00:06:27,660
Either way, I won't say anything.

108
00:06:29,330 --> 00:06:30,930
Okay. Thank you.

109
00:06:31,730 --> 00:06:32,730
You can leave now.

110
00:06:43,640 --> 00:06:44,640
Oh my goodness.

111
00:06:45,710 --> 00:06:47,210
I can't believe Kang Jun Ho
is Chae Hwa Young's son.

112
00:06:47,750 --> 00:06:48,750
Oh my.

113
00:06:49,450 --> 00:06:51,780
I mean, she had her own son,

114
00:06:52,350 --> 00:06:54,790
so why did she steal someone else's twin?

115
00:06:56,820 --> 00:06:58,960
That Chae Hwa Young is one scary woman.

116
00:07:03,830 --> 00:07:05,630
You just heard everything, didn't you?

117
00:07:06,660 --> 00:07:07,830
Well...

118
00:07:08,030 --> 00:07:09,500
But Jang Mi,

119
00:07:10,170 --> 00:07:12,670
is Kang Jun Ho really
Chae Hwa Young's son?

120
00:07:13,200 --> 00:07:16,240
I just can't believe it,
even after hearing it myself.

121
00:07:16,310 --> 00:07:18,280
You heard what Seo Rin asked for too,
right?

122
00:07:19,040 --> 00:07:20,040
Please keep it a secret.

123
00:07:20,510 --> 00:07:23,710
Right. Of course. I understand.

124
00:07:33,060 --> 00:07:34,060
Hong Ju?

125
00:07:34,330 --> 00:07:36,890
- I've got big news.
- What? Jun Ho is...

126
00:07:39,030 --> 00:07:41,030
really CEO Chae's son?

127
00:07:42,500 --> 00:07:44,870
Of course, I had no idea either.

128
00:07:44,870 --> 00:07:46,640
CEO Chae is unbelievable.

129
00:07:46,970 --> 00:07:50,580
She tried to marry her biological son
and the daughter she raised.

130
00:07:50,640 --> 00:07:51,640
Team Leader Jin.

131
00:07:52,710 --> 00:07:53,710
Mom, I have to go.

132
00:07:54,780 --> 00:07:55,780
Yes, Baek Ho?

133
00:07:57,350 --> 00:07:59,250
You seem to enjoy gossiping
about other people,

134
00:07:59,850 --> 00:08:00,850
but I suggest you refrain.

135
00:08:01,520 --> 00:08:03,590
So, you knew about it too, Baek Ho?

136
00:08:04,620 --> 00:08:07,430
- Unbelievable.
- Don't be so smug. It's offensive.

137
00:08:07,860 --> 00:08:10,030
Turning my family's affairs into gossip.

138
00:08:10,030 --> 00:08:11,700
I'm sorry.

139
00:08:12,200 --> 00:08:14,430
It's just that it was so shocking.

140
00:08:15,070 --> 00:08:17,500
CEO Chae really does always
cross the line.

141
00:08:26,980 --> 00:08:29,550
Seo Rin, now you have to do me a favor.

142
00:08:30,050 --> 00:08:31,950
- What is it?
- Our dad.

143
00:08:32,580 --> 00:08:34,420
Wait, not "our" dad, I guess.

144
00:08:35,720 --> 00:08:38,460
You said you had evidence
in the Oh Bok Gil murder case, right?

145
00:08:39,020 --> 00:08:40,020
What?

146
00:08:40,590 --> 00:08:41,960
You mean the lipstick USB?

147
00:08:43,260 --> 00:08:46,230
But I said I didn't know where it was.

148
00:08:46,430 --> 00:08:47,900
You said there was something else
besides that.

149
00:08:48,430 --> 00:08:51,570
What is it?
You said you would tell me everything.

150
00:08:52,040 --> 00:08:54,240
You said you'd tell me so Chae Hwa Young
could pay for her crimes.

151
00:08:56,410 --> 00:08:57,710
So where is it?

152
00:08:58,810 --> 00:08:59,810
There's...

153
00:09:03,380 --> 00:09:04,550
a wrench.

154
00:09:05,350 --> 00:09:07,690
- It's probably the murder weapon.
- A wrench?

155
00:09:10,860 --> 00:09:12,790
So you're saying she hit our dad
with that?

156
00:09:12,860 --> 00:09:15,630
Shit. How would I know?

157
00:09:15,630 --> 00:09:17,560
Anyway, I overheard them talking.

158
00:09:18,200 --> 00:09:21,400
So where is it?

159
00:09:21,930 --> 00:09:24,600
If we find the murder weapon,
we can make Chae Hwa Young pay.

160
00:09:25,840 --> 00:09:28,670
But the thing is,
I don't know where it is either.

161
00:09:29,070 --> 00:09:30,980
What? You don't know?

162
00:09:32,610 --> 00:09:34,850
Don't tell me,

163
00:09:35,850 --> 00:09:37,010
you know everything...

164
00:09:37,420 --> 00:09:39,150
and are covering for Chae Hwa Young?

165
00:09:40,020 --> 00:09:42,520
Is it always about you, Oh Jang Mi?

166
00:09:43,250 --> 00:09:46,320
Oh Bok Gil may have been your father,
but Chae Hwa Young was my mother.

167
00:09:46,920 --> 00:09:49,690
Whether she's a murderer or not,
whether she tried to harm me or not,

168
00:09:50,160 --> 00:09:52,900
for 30 years, I knew her as my mother.

169
00:09:53,600 --> 00:09:56,970
If you were in my shoes,
could you handle this so easily?

170
00:09:58,400 --> 00:10:01,570
One day, I hate her so much
I want to kill her,

171
00:10:02,270 --> 00:10:04,910
and the next, I wake up and miss her.

172
00:10:06,140 --> 00:10:08,780
That's who Chae Hwa Young is to me.
Got it?

173
00:10:10,180 --> 00:10:11,180
Alright.

174
00:10:11,820 --> 00:10:12,850
I'm sorry, Seo Rin.

175
00:10:13,750 --> 00:10:15,590
Right. To you,
Chae Hwa Young was your mother.

176
00:10:17,150 --> 00:10:20,220
But Chae Hwa Young
never saw you as her daughter.

177
00:10:20,790 --> 00:10:23,090
You were just a stepping stone,
a tool for her ambition.

178
00:10:23,190 --> 00:10:24,800
I know, okay? I know.

179
00:10:25,430 --> 00:10:27,600
But knowing something and feeling it
are two different things.

180
00:10:29,530 --> 00:10:31,940
Anyway, just go home for today.

181
00:10:33,270 --> 00:10:34,840
I don't want to talk about this
anymore today.

182
00:10:35,140 --> 00:10:36,940
Okay. Get some rest.

183
00:10:44,150 --> 00:10:45,150
Seong Sil...

184
00:10:45,920 --> 00:10:46,950
Seong Sil.

185
00:10:48,720 --> 00:10:52,490
Chairman, are you still sleeping?
Have some fruit.

186
00:10:52,590 --> 00:10:53,790
Seong Sil.

187
00:10:54,990 --> 00:10:55,990
Don't go.

188
00:10:56,790 --> 00:10:57,930
Seong Sil.

189
00:11:03,330 --> 00:11:05,070
What? Seong Sil?

190
00:11:05,570 --> 00:11:07,070
Who is this tramp he is calling?

191
00:11:09,110 --> 00:11:11,110
Have some fruit. Honey!

192
00:11:12,640 --> 00:11:13,640
What?

193
00:11:18,850 --> 00:11:20,620
What were you dreaming about?

194
00:11:22,320 --> 00:11:25,290
Were you dreaming of a woman
you're dying to see?

195
00:11:27,090 --> 00:11:28,090
Be quiet.

196
00:11:33,560 --> 00:11:36,530
What? Father was calling out
another woman's name?

197
00:11:36,800 --> 00:11:40,440
Yes. He was going, "Seong Sil."

198
00:11:41,240 --> 00:11:42,570
"Don't go, Seong Sil."

199
00:11:43,370 --> 00:11:46,410
He was calling her name so pathetically...

200
00:11:46,610 --> 00:11:48,550
that I couldn't stand watching him.

201
00:11:49,110 --> 00:11:53,320
For him to call her name in his sleep,
she must be someone important.

202
00:11:53,850 --> 00:11:55,350
When I find out...

203
00:11:55,690 --> 00:12:00,290
how close this Seong Sil woman was to him,
I'll make her pay.

204
00:12:01,090 --> 00:12:02,090
Seong Sil?

205
00:12:03,030 --> 00:12:07,600
I can't let Seong Sil take my place.
No way!

206
00:12:08,270 --> 00:12:09,270
Seong Sil?

207
00:12:09,800 --> 00:12:10,900
Who could that be?

208
00:12:17,880 --> 00:12:19,610
I didn't mean to overhear.

209
00:12:20,240 --> 00:12:22,180
Who is this Seong Sil person?

210
00:12:22,180 --> 00:12:23,750
That's what I want to know.

211
00:12:25,850 --> 00:12:27,950
What's that you have there?

212
00:12:29,850 --> 00:12:32,660
Grandfather told me to give this
to you, ma'am.

213
00:12:35,230 --> 00:12:37,130
I guess he feels bad
for snapping at me earlier.

214
00:12:37,930 --> 00:12:41,470
The Chairman sure knows
how to handle women.

215
00:12:41,770 --> 00:12:44,000
Oh Jang Mi. By the way,

216
00:12:44,100 --> 00:12:47,400
who gave birth to Ma Dong Seok, your dad?

217
00:12:47,670 --> 00:12:50,210
What? You mean my grandmother's name?

218
00:12:50,880 --> 00:12:51,880
Yes.

219
00:12:52,410 --> 00:12:55,150
That could be it. My husband's first wife.

220
00:12:56,880 --> 00:12:58,980
I've never really thought
about my grandmother's name.

221
00:12:59,680 --> 00:13:02,990
- Maybe I should ask him.
- No, don't. Later.

222
00:13:03,520 --> 00:13:06,660
If you ask him now,
he'll accuse me of putting you up to it.

223
00:13:16,230 --> 00:13:17,230
Dad.

224
00:13:20,800 --> 00:13:21,810
You've been drinking.

225
00:13:22,870 --> 00:13:24,180
Father, why would you do that?

226
00:13:25,310 --> 00:13:28,980
Instead of helping your son get ahead,

227
00:13:30,080 --> 00:13:31,950
was your love life that important to you?

228
00:13:32,780 --> 00:13:35,720
Why would you have an affair
and ruin everything?

229
00:13:36,450 --> 00:13:39,160
If you're drunk, you should just
go to your room and sleep it off.

230
00:13:39,420 --> 00:13:40,620
What's with this drunken scene?

231
00:13:41,430 --> 00:13:42,890
Jun Ho. Stop it, all right?

232
00:13:46,660 --> 00:13:50,070
Why are you drinking
when you know you shouldn't be?

233
00:13:50,070 --> 00:13:51,200
Let's go in, Jun Ho.

234
00:13:51,440 --> 00:13:52,440
Let go of me!

235
00:13:55,010 --> 00:13:57,040
Because of your precious little affair,

236
00:13:57,470 --> 00:13:59,380
CEO Chae Hwa Young was
kicked out of her home...

237
00:13:59,810 --> 00:14:01,580
and fired from her company.

238
00:14:02,650 --> 00:14:03,680
Are you satisfied now?

239
00:14:04,110 --> 00:14:06,150
What? CEO Chae got kicked out?

240
00:14:06,450 --> 00:14:09,550
Chae Hwa Young had it coming
for a number of reasons.

241
00:14:10,250 --> 00:14:14,590
She had an affair,
stole a twin, and ruined a marriage.

242
00:14:15,460 --> 00:14:16,590
Serves her right.

243
00:14:16,860 --> 00:14:20,030
Mom, you shouldn't be saying that.

244
00:14:20,030 --> 00:14:21,370
Calm down.

245
00:14:22,230 --> 00:14:23,230
Let's just go inside.

246
00:14:27,870 --> 00:14:31,380
Look at the mess our family is in
because of that woman, Chae Hwa Young!

247
00:14:32,880 --> 00:14:35,450
You're a terrible judge of character.

248
00:14:35,850 --> 00:14:39,180
If you had to have an affair,
why her of all people?

249
00:14:40,520 --> 00:14:41,920
Get your head on straight now.

250
00:14:52,100 --> 00:14:53,160
Did Hwa Young...

251
00:14:53,860 --> 00:14:56,370
really get fired because of me?

252
00:15:00,570 --> 00:15:02,440
(CEO Chae)

253
00:15:07,750 --> 00:15:10,010
Yes, this is Kang Nam Bong.

254
00:15:13,180 --> 00:15:14,180
Kang Baek Ho.

255
00:15:14,750 --> 00:15:15,920
Are you happy now?

256
00:15:16,920 --> 00:15:20,190
- Life's easy when it all goes your way.
- Jun Ho.

257
00:15:20,860 --> 00:15:24,160
- Stop whining and face reality.
- Why is everything so easy for you?

258
00:15:25,530 --> 00:15:28,700
Then again, you were born
with a silver spoon in your mouth,

259
00:15:29,470 --> 00:15:31,000
so I guess nothing's
ever been hard for you...

260
00:15:32,170 --> 00:15:33,540
because you're their real son.

261
00:15:33,770 --> 00:15:34,970
Jun Ho, please...

262
00:15:35,710 --> 00:15:37,910
stop this nonsense about me
being a real son and you being adopted.

263
00:15:38,540 --> 00:15:39,780
Our mom...

264
00:15:40,080 --> 00:15:42,950
always gave you herbal medicine
because you were struggling,

265
00:15:43,480 --> 00:15:46,120
but when I tried to take just one,
she treated me like a thief.

266
00:15:46,680 --> 00:15:47,890
And when you were...

267
00:15:48,350 --> 00:15:51,960
in the hospital with burns,
Dad was so worried he didn't sleep a wink.

268
00:15:52,720 --> 00:15:54,660
If anything,
they did more for you, not less.

269
00:15:54,730 --> 00:15:58,100
For someone born starving for affection,
even that isn't enough.

270
00:15:58,830 --> 00:16:00,200
- What?
- If you knew...

271
00:16:00,200 --> 00:16:01,830
whose blood runs through my veins,

272
00:16:03,070 --> 00:16:04,670
you wouldn't dare talk to me like that.

273
00:16:08,710 --> 00:16:09,970
You already know, don't you?

274
00:16:11,380 --> 00:16:12,740
You know who my birth mother is.

275
00:16:13,780 --> 00:16:15,350
- Jun Ho.
- Of course,

276
00:16:16,080 --> 00:16:17,610
you must have heard it from Jang Mi.

277
00:16:18,680 --> 00:16:19,680
Right.

278
00:16:20,280 --> 00:16:22,890
That horrible woman's blood
runs through my veins.

279
00:16:24,690 --> 00:16:26,720
You'll never know how filthy that feels.

280
00:16:28,460 --> 00:16:31,230
Whatever anyone says, we are your family.

281
00:16:31,400 --> 00:16:33,130
Think of all the time we spent together...

282
00:16:33,900 --> 00:16:35,200
and all the memories.

283
00:16:36,930 --> 00:16:37,940
No.

284
00:16:38,570 --> 00:16:39,900
You can't possibly understand.

285
00:16:41,610 --> 00:16:42,640
Never.

286
00:17:03,730 --> 00:17:06,500
- Thank you for coming.
- Why did you call me?

287
00:17:06,960 --> 00:17:09,130
I had no intention of seeing you again.

288
00:17:09,970 --> 00:17:14,240
Everyone is turning on me,
and they've all abandoned me.

289
00:17:14,970 --> 00:17:17,510
Did you really steal one of the twins,
Hwa Young?

290
00:17:18,440 --> 00:17:21,010
I heard it,
but I just couldn't believe it.

291
00:17:21,950 --> 00:17:26,920
I don't know how much to believe,
or if I can believe all that Baek Ho said.

292
00:17:27,320 --> 00:17:28,820
I honestly have no idea.

293
00:17:29,020 --> 00:17:30,650
So I came to confirm it for myself...

294
00:17:31,050 --> 00:17:32,220
to see if it's all true.

295
00:17:32,290 --> 00:17:34,360
Nam Bong, you don't actually
believe that, do you?

296
00:17:34,790 --> 00:17:36,190
You don't, right?

297
00:17:38,000 --> 00:17:42,170
Right now, Lawyer Kang would believe
anything Oh Jang Mi says.

298
00:17:42,970 --> 00:17:45,370
She's always hated me.

299
00:17:45,370 --> 00:17:47,500
That's why she's trying to frame me.

300
00:17:50,840 --> 00:17:51,940
Today,

301
00:17:52,810 --> 00:17:54,780
I was just hoping you would comfort me.

302
00:17:56,850 --> 00:17:59,520
After Chairman Ma threw me out
of Dream Hotel,

303
00:17:59,780 --> 00:18:03,920
I lost my CEO position,
and I have nowhere else to turn.

304
00:18:04,490 --> 00:18:07,660
You were my only hope, Nam Bong.
My only safe harbor.

305
00:18:08,860 --> 00:18:12,330
That's why I called you,
even though I knew I was imposing.

306
00:18:14,970 --> 00:18:16,770
I should never have fallen
in love with you.

307
00:18:17,770 --> 00:18:20,670
If I'd known I would lose everything,
I never would've gotten involved with you.

308
00:18:23,840 --> 00:18:27,780
Can Chairman Ma really not find it in him
to forgive you about me?

309
00:18:28,080 --> 00:18:29,610
No matter how much I begged
for his forgiveness,

310
00:18:30,080 --> 00:18:32,220
he used my affair as an excuse
to drive me out.

311
00:18:32,480 --> 00:18:35,250
He's just ambitious and wants to replace
everyone with his own people.

312
00:18:35,420 --> 00:18:37,290
I only realized that when it was too late.

313
00:18:39,220 --> 00:18:40,220
I just don't...

314
00:18:41,120 --> 00:18:42,790
I just don't understand.

315
00:18:42,790 --> 00:18:44,660
You've always been in academia.

316
00:18:45,000 --> 00:18:47,430
You could never understand
a cutthroat organization like this.

317
00:18:48,330 --> 00:18:49,770
How desperate do you think I was...

318
00:18:50,230 --> 00:18:51,570
to accuse you...

319
00:18:52,340 --> 00:18:55,210
of being a stalker
when I didn't mean a word of it?

320
00:18:56,640 --> 00:18:59,980
To be honest, I was deeply hurt by that.

321
00:19:01,040 --> 00:19:02,110
I'm sure you were.

322
00:19:03,380 --> 00:19:04,780
You had every right to be.

323
00:19:05,850 --> 00:19:08,350
You know that's not how
I really feel, don't you?

324
00:19:12,360 --> 00:19:13,390
The truth is,

325
00:19:14,630 --> 00:19:17,460
there's something I need to confess.

326
00:19:19,000 --> 00:19:20,000
What is it?

327
00:19:20,630 --> 00:19:22,100
A confession?

328
00:19:22,370 --> 00:19:23,870
Try not to be too shocked.

329
00:19:25,470 --> 00:19:27,870
Your son, Kang Jun Ho.

330
00:19:29,540 --> 00:19:32,180
I'm his birth mother.

331
00:19:35,110 --> 00:19:36,110
Is that...

332
00:19:36,850 --> 00:19:39,020
Is that really true?

333
00:19:39,420 --> 00:19:41,050
I'm sorry I couldn't tell you sooner.

334
00:19:43,320 --> 00:19:44,350
I...

335
00:19:45,060 --> 00:19:46,660
I'm so in love with you, Nam Bong.

336
00:19:47,820 --> 00:19:48,830
But...

337
00:19:49,530 --> 00:19:51,960
when I realized my son
was your Kang Jun Ho,

338
00:19:52,760 --> 00:19:56,070
I couldn't be with you
as your lover anymore.

339
00:19:59,400 --> 00:20:00,400
So that was it.

340
00:20:01,170 --> 00:20:02,240
That's right.

341
00:20:03,140 --> 00:20:04,980
So that's why you pushed me away.

342
00:20:05,680 --> 00:20:06,980
It all makes sense now.

343
00:20:07,380 --> 00:20:09,510
- So...
- You see now, don't you?

344
00:20:11,650 --> 00:20:14,080
Now you know how I truly feel, don't you?

345
00:20:16,320 --> 00:20:17,960
I love you, Nam Bong.

346
00:20:18,760 --> 00:20:19,760
Hwa Young...

347
00:20:20,420 --> 00:20:22,360
How can this be?

348
00:20:29,300 --> 00:20:30,300
Mom.

349
00:20:31,970 --> 00:20:36,710
Jang Mi is here. My pretty Jang Mi.
You're not going anywhere now.

350
00:20:37,740 --> 00:20:39,140
I'm so happy, Jang Mi.

351
00:20:39,910 --> 00:20:44,580
That's right, Mom. I'm not going anywhere.
I'll stay with you for a long, long time.

352
00:20:44,850 --> 00:20:46,220
Jang Mi, I'm glad you're here.

353
00:20:46,850 --> 00:20:47,850
Tae Pyung.

354
00:20:48,190 --> 00:20:50,550
- Where's Tae Sook?
- She's not back from the restaurant yet.

355
00:20:50,850 --> 00:20:52,020
Busy making money.

356
00:20:52,390 --> 00:20:55,190
(Suk Hee's Side Dishes)

357
00:21:00,900 --> 00:21:02,630
Grandma, you're so good at this.

358
00:21:04,900 --> 00:21:06,440
You know what, Mom?

359
00:21:07,070 --> 00:21:11,110
Even if your memories fade,
they say the body never forgets.

360
00:21:11,440 --> 00:21:13,340
It's called muscle memory.

361
00:21:14,040 --> 00:21:16,980
For you, it's your instinct
to protect me and Seo Rin,

362
00:21:17,050 --> 00:21:19,720
and your amazing skills in the kitchen.
They haven't changed.

363
00:21:20,080 --> 00:21:24,150
Your muscles are even smarter
and more amazing than your mind, Mom.

364
00:21:25,120 --> 00:21:28,360
Suk Hee is smart. Suk Hee is amazing.

365
00:21:29,760 --> 00:21:32,430
Jang Mi, go buy Bo Ra a snack.

366
00:21:32,560 --> 00:21:34,800
Grandma, I want some strawberries.

367
00:21:35,100 --> 00:21:38,140
You do? Let's buy some tomorrow, okay?

368
00:21:39,670 --> 00:21:42,340
Look who's talking, you bag of bones!

369
00:21:42,340 --> 00:21:44,240
- Goodness.
- Who are you calling a fatty?

370
00:21:44,370 --> 00:21:47,440
Don't you know I can't stand it
when people talk back?

371
00:21:47,510 --> 00:21:49,180
Hey, let go of me!

372
00:21:51,150 --> 00:21:52,720
Why you...

373
00:21:53,620 --> 00:21:54,820
Hey!

374
00:21:54,820 --> 00:21:56,490
That lady isn't backing down
when the vendor is that big.

375
00:21:58,020 --> 00:22:00,790
- No fighting.
- Hey!

376
00:22:00,990 --> 00:22:05,100
Let go of me! You want to die?
I'll kill you!

377
00:22:05,160 --> 00:22:09,200
Criminal Act, Article 260.
Assault, Paragraph 1.

378
00:22:09,700 --> 00:22:12,400
Any person who commits assault
against another...

379
00:22:12,800 --> 00:22:16,310
shall be imprisoned for up to two years
or fined up to 5,000 dollars.

380
00:22:16,640 --> 00:22:17,810
Article Two.

381
00:22:17,810 --> 00:22:20,640
If the Paragraph 1 assault is
against one's own...

382
00:22:21,080 --> 00:22:23,110
- or a spouse's direct ascendant,
- Darn it.

383
00:22:23,580 --> 00:22:26,920
the penalty is up to 5 years' imprisonment
or a fine of up to 7,000 dollars.

384
00:22:28,450 --> 00:22:30,390
- Mom.
- Paragraph Three.

385
00:22:30,390 --> 00:22:32,160
Prosecution for the offenses
in Paragraphs 1 and 2...

386
00:22:32,620 --> 00:22:36,530
cannot proceed if the victim
clearly states they do not want it.

387
00:22:40,130 --> 00:22:41,130
Mom.

388
00:22:42,300 --> 00:22:43,570
Are you yourself again?

389
00:22:46,040 --> 00:22:48,070
Fighting makes you a bad person.

390
00:22:50,440 --> 00:22:51,710
Jang Mi is pretty.

391
00:22:52,280 --> 00:22:53,310
Jang Mi is good.

392
00:22:54,540 --> 00:22:55,650
Gosh, you gave me a scare.

393
00:22:55,980 --> 00:22:58,950
For a minute there, I thought
the half-wit had turned into a genius.

394
00:22:59,550 --> 00:23:00,550
Hey!

395
00:23:01,150 --> 00:23:02,890
Why you... What?

396
00:23:03,950 --> 00:23:05,020
- Let me go!
- I'm scared.

397
00:23:05,020 --> 00:23:06,060
Still not finished?

398
00:23:21,140 --> 00:23:22,470
Oh Jang Mi...

399
00:23:23,270 --> 00:23:24,640
She's coming in with Baek Ho?

400
00:23:24,980 --> 00:23:27,610
What is going on?
Why are those two walking in together?

401
00:23:28,610 --> 00:23:32,220
Could the Chairman really be
planning to give Oh Jang Mi something?

402
00:23:43,190 --> 00:23:44,190
Ma Seo Rin.

403
00:23:47,130 --> 00:23:49,330
Do you really think this is the time
to be kicking back and listening to music?

404
00:23:50,830 --> 00:23:51,870
Are you crazy?

405
00:23:52,340 --> 00:23:55,070
The Chairman is with Baek Ho right now,

406
00:23:55,070 --> 00:23:56,510
telling him to give Oh Jang Mi
a share of it all.

407
00:23:57,370 --> 00:24:00,410
- He's going to give her your share, too.
- What?

408
00:24:05,950 --> 00:24:10,520
That's right. I'll provoke Ma Seo Rin
and have her get rid of Oh Jang Mi.

409
00:24:12,790 --> 00:24:14,320
All right, that's good.

410
00:24:14,320 --> 00:24:17,830
Now all Jang Mi has to do is sign.

411
00:24:18,090 --> 00:24:21,460
Yes. This is the paperwork
to officially register her as Ma Jang Mi.

412
00:24:22,630 --> 00:24:24,130
This is the deed to the building.

413
00:24:24,730 --> 00:24:27,440
This transfers a portion
of the shares of Dream to you.

414
00:24:28,370 --> 00:24:31,610
- Grandfather, this is...
- What's wrong?

415
00:24:32,010 --> 00:24:35,150
Are you reluctant to become Ma Jang Mi?

416
00:24:35,150 --> 00:24:36,380
It's not that.

417
00:24:37,680 --> 00:24:41,990
I'll change my name after I catch
the culprit and clear my father's name.

418
00:24:43,450 --> 00:24:44,450
Stubborn girl.

419
00:24:45,120 --> 00:24:46,520
If that's what you want, then go ahead.

420
00:24:47,320 --> 00:24:50,390
But you have to accept...

421
00:24:51,090 --> 00:24:52,860
these stocks and this property.

422
00:24:53,130 --> 00:24:54,800
It's what this old man wants for you.

423
00:24:55,200 --> 00:24:58,800
And tomorrow, bring your mother
and the rest of your family here.

424
00:24:59,070 --> 00:25:01,040
This old man wants
to treat you all to a meal.

425
00:25:01,770 --> 00:25:03,440
Yes, I will.

426
00:25:05,110 --> 00:25:08,310
(Donor, Donee)

427
00:25:09,380 --> 00:25:11,850
My goodness,
how much is all of that worth?

428
00:25:13,020 --> 00:25:14,620
A building right in the middle of Gangnam?

429
00:25:14,680 --> 00:25:16,520
Isn't that more than what Seo Rin got?

430
00:25:17,150 --> 00:25:18,150
Grandfather!

431
00:25:20,220 --> 00:25:21,220
Grandfather.

432
00:25:21,690 --> 00:25:24,230
How could you give her something better
than what you gave me?

433
00:25:24,490 --> 00:25:26,830
I'm supposed to be your favorite!

434
00:25:26,960 --> 00:25:28,130
Why does...

435
00:25:28,370 --> 00:25:31,370
Why does everyone only like Oh Jang Mi?

436
00:25:31,770 --> 00:25:34,170
Why is everyone taking what's mine?

437
00:25:34,240 --> 00:25:37,570
Seo Rin! What is this insolent attitude?

438
00:25:38,410 --> 00:25:40,010
You're being so unfair, Grandfather.

439
00:25:40,440 --> 00:25:42,750
Seo Rin, calm down. Ma Seo Rin.

440
00:25:43,280 --> 00:25:46,120
I have never been greedy
for Grandfather's wealth.

441
00:25:46,280 --> 00:25:48,550
If you're against it,
I don't have to take any of this.

442
00:25:49,220 --> 00:25:52,760
Really? So that's your game?
Playing the noble saint?

443
00:25:52,820 --> 00:25:54,120
It's not like that.

444
00:25:54,420 --> 00:25:57,090
I can't be greedy for something
that was never mine to begin with.

445
00:25:57,690 --> 00:26:01,060
I'm grateful to Grandfather, but...

446
00:26:01,130 --> 00:26:02,200
Really?

447
00:26:02,400 --> 00:26:03,830
Then you won't mind if I rip this up,
will you?

448
00:26:06,840 --> 00:26:08,840
Why are you taking what's mine?

449
00:26:09,170 --> 00:26:11,570
I won't give it up. I'll give you nothing.
It's all mine!

450
00:26:11,640 --> 00:26:12,640
Seo Rin!

451
00:26:13,380 --> 00:26:16,580
How do you expect to run Dream
with a character like that?

452
00:26:16,710 --> 00:26:17,710
Grandfather.

453
00:26:18,480 --> 00:26:20,720
You were always on my side.

454
00:26:20,920 --> 00:26:22,690
When my own mother showed me
no affection...

455
00:26:22,850 --> 00:26:26,860
and was so cold and harsh,
your love was real, wasn't it?

456
00:26:27,560 --> 00:26:30,690
It was real,
so how could you do this to me?

457
00:26:30,890 --> 00:26:32,960
Jang Mi is my granddaughter too.

458
00:26:33,460 --> 00:26:38,130
Even if you tear up that document,
I can have another drawn up for Jang Mi.

459
00:26:38,200 --> 00:26:41,770
Grandfather, please don't.
You're hurting Seo Rin.

460
00:26:42,910 --> 00:26:45,940
Oh Jang Mi, you're so perfect, aren't you?

461
00:26:47,980 --> 00:26:49,550
Enough.

462
00:26:49,610 --> 00:26:52,520
Seo Rin, what am I going to do with you?

463
00:26:58,120 --> 00:26:59,120
Seo Rin.

464
00:26:59,760 --> 00:27:02,990
Don't worry.
I won't accept Grandfather's offer.

465
00:27:03,330 --> 00:27:05,660
If you're going to resent me
this much over it,

466
00:27:06,160 --> 00:27:07,660
I'd be truly heartbroken.

467
00:27:07,730 --> 00:27:09,800
You're really not going to take
what Grandfather's giving you?

468
00:27:10,330 --> 00:27:12,340
You're not going to be secretly
signing papers...

469
00:27:12,700 --> 00:27:14,300
and making deals behind my back, are you?

470
00:27:14,400 --> 00:27:18,310
You have everything.
What are you so insecure about?

471
00:27:18,840 --> 00:27:20,310
I already told you.

472
00:27:20,740 --> 00:27:22,410
I have absolutely no intention
of taking what's yours.

473
00:27:22,610 --> 00:27:24,150
Then why did you even come here today?

474
00:27:24,480 --> 00:27:27,520
If I hadn't stopped you,
you would have signed it.

475
00:27:27,520 --> 00:27:29,050
That's not what was happening.

476
00:27:29,250 --> 00:27:30,950
What will it take for you to believe me?

477
00:27:32,120 --> 00:27:34,860
I'm bringing our mother to have a meal
with Grandfather tomorrow.

478
00:27:35,260 --> 00:27:37,560
So please, stop holding a grudge.

479
00:27:54,380 --> 00:27:55,380
Welcome.

480
00:28:31,010 --> 00:28:32,580
(The First Man)

481
00:28:32,680 --> 00:28:34,420
I heard that cost more than
300,000 dollars.

482
00:28:36,920 --> 00:28:38,790
That man is evil. He's terrifying.

483
00:28:38,790 --> 00:28:42,330
I intend to formally ask the Chairman
for his permission for us to marry.

484
00:28:42,490 --> 00:28:43,890
Come back to the company now.

485
00:28:44,190 --> 00:28:47,000
Or else Oh Jang Mi is going
to take it all.

486
00:28:47,230 --> 00:28:50,730
You're saying Chae Hwa Young is the one
who gave birth to Jun Ho?

487
00:28:50,870 --> 00:28:53,740
And Professor Kang Nam Bong
knew about it too?

488
00:28:53,900 --> 00:28:55,570
What do you think you're doing?

489
00:28:58,840 --> 00:29:00,840
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
